headline: Fifth Third Bank to Decrease Prime Lending Rate to 7.25%
summary: CINCINNATI, September 17, 2025--Fifth Third Bank, National Association (Nasdaq: FITB) today announced it will decrease its prime lending rate to 7.25%, effective immediately.
